38629 - Update site data settings label. r=nhnt11\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: EgBzUyv3eRh", "files": ["browser/components/preferences/in-content/privacy.xul", "browser/components/preferences/siteDataSettings.xul", "browser/locales/en-US/chrome/browser/preferences/advanced.dtd", "browser/locales/en-US/chrome/browser/preferences/siteDataSettings.dtd"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "495671109f3aad195cd7987cafe800c79dcb7175", "parents": ["3bc1743ad418e8bfebfe4a2323d2e3519ba82891"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Felipe Gomes \u003cfelipc@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1426362 - Display status of policy engine in about:support. r=bytesized\n\nThis also changes the const values of nsIEnterprisePolicies to a more common numbering pattern.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: CKs1TWGMqJN", "files": ["toolkit/components/enterprisepolicies/nsIEnterprisePolicies.idl", "toolkit/content/aboutSupport.js", "toolkit/content/aboutSupport.xhtml", "toolkit/locales/en-US/chrome/global/aboutSupport.dtd", "toolkit/locales/en-US/chrome/global/aboutSupport.properties", "toolkit/modules/Troubleshoot.jsm", "toolkit/modules/tests/browser/browser_Troubleshoot.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "476e0758eb1c2736ef1c442cd70a8df6d1113897", "parents": ["495671109f3aad195cd7987cafe800c79dcb7175"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Francois Marier \u003cfrancois@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1442486 - Mark LookupCacheV4 as primed after creating it. r=gcp\n\nRegenActiveTables() relies on mPrimed being set correctly and so\nthe V4 lookup cache should behave the same way as the V2 one.\n\nThe V2 lookup cache on the other hand was unnecessarily setting\nmPrimed to true twice.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: LwNdI9DTqZ7", "files": ["toolkit/components/url-classifier/Classifier.cpp", "toolkit/components/url-classifier/LookupCache.cpp", "toolkit/components/url-classifier/LookupCacheV4.cpp", "toolkit/components/url-classifier/nsUrlClassifierDBService.cpp"], "git_