, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "archaeopteryx@coole-files.de"}, "8813": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mihai Tabara \u003cmtabara@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1443104 - fix update folder in bouncer submission release job. r=jlorenzo,Callek a=release CLOSED TREE\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: E1vqqaG1PE9", "files": ["taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/bouncer_submission.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f149ea88f20108dec9d7937b8f45138744461150", "parents": ["13a58c13967f9e10e36aac6f72f2f02429e959ee"], "tags": []}], "date": 1520265401, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "mtabara@mozilla.com"}, "8814": {"changesets": [{"author": "Nicolas Chevobbe \u003cnchevobbe@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "FIREFOX_59b_RELBRANCH", "desc": "Bug 1441868 - Remove unused css properties. r=bgrins a=RyanVM\n\nThis also reveals a regression on the border color for warning and error messages\nin dark mode, which is fixed by this patch.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: H24hOYVhpr7", "files": ["devtools/client/themes/webconsole.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8abde869985b839392a2a64348273579076c374a", "parents": ["d06407068b75e11bd7d553de10a2b381929edddf"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Paul Adenot \u003cpaul@paul.cx\u003e", "branch": "FIREFOX_59b_RELBRANCH", "desc": "Bug 1426129 - Take a reference to `this` when calling methods asynchronously in CameraChild.cpp. r=pehrsons a=lizzard", "files": ["dom/media/systemservices/CamerasChild.cpp", "dom/media/systemservices/CamerasChild.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d613c28bb2fc2771d381e43b3b7f8e25553b50a7", "parents": ["8abde869985b839392a2a64348273579076c374a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "James Teh \u003cjteh@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "FIREFOX_59b_RELBRANCH", "desc": "Bug 1440257: Ensure that mscom::MainThreadInvoker gets cleaned up very soon after it finishes executing. r=aklotz a=lizzard\n\nMainThreadInvoker queues both a Gecko runnable and an APC to the main thread to deal with different ways in which the main thread can block.\nHowever, the main thread doesn't check for APCs very often any more.\nThis means that the APC's reference to the SyncRunnable doesn't get cleaned up for a long time, thus leaking memory.\nTo work around this, we:\n1. Queue an APC wich does the actual work.\n2. Post a Gecko runnable (which always runs).\nIf the APC hasn't run, the Gecko runnable runs it.\nOtherwise, it does nothing.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: L0P4rMBnlaZ", "files": ["ipc/mscom/MainThreadInvoker.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5da6d8b0b9714aa2a9556eb79f6533451d7500c0", "parents": ["d613c28bb2fc2771d381e43b3b7f8e25553b50a7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Chris Pearce \u003ccpearce@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "FIREFOX_59b_RELBRANCH", "desc": "Bug 1441153 - Block cross origin redirects after media channel setup for wav. r=jya a=lizzard", "files": ["dom/media/ChannelMediaDecoder.cpp", "dom/media/ChannelMediaDecoder.h", "dom/media/DecoderTraits.cpp", "dom/media/DecoderTraits.h", "dom/media/MediaDecoder.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "01ca4a01f130c63dd169cf1a58b66fe1b7881d2d", "parents": ["5da6d8b0b9714aa2a9556eb79f6533451d7500c0"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Pehrson \u003cpehrsons@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "FIREFOX_59b_RELBRANCH", "desc": "Bug 1441145 - Hack the frame rotation through to CamerasParent and CamerasChild. r=jib a=lizzard\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 1UL1Ixkzl86", "files": ["media/webrtc/trunk/webrtc/modules/video_capture/video_capture_impl.cc"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5ed282b8b20d143d6193e547825dbb319e2e4c0e", "parents": ["01ca4a01f130c63dd169cf1a58b66fe1b7881d2d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Pehrson \u003cpehrsons@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "FIREFOX_59b_RELBRANCH", "desc": "Bug 1441145 - Swap width and height in target capability if the frame is rotated. r=jib a=lizzard\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 3QO3W0J3b6G", "files": ["dom/media/webrtc/MediaEngineRemoteVideoSource.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "52bcd064838a6976f80173ce3bcd924c8fb0e6ad", "parents": ["5ed282b8b20d143d6193e547825dbb319e2e4c0e"], "tags": []}], "date": 1520277936, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "archaeopteryx@coole-files.de"}, "8815": {"changesets": [{"author": "Sebastian Hengst \u003carchaeopteryx@coole-files.de\u003e", "branch": "FIREFOX_59b_RELBRANCH", "desc": "Backed out changeset d613c28bb2fc (bug 1426129) for crashing in mda's dom/media/tests/mochitest/test_enumerateDevices.html. a=backout CLOSED TREE", "files": ["dom/media/systemservices/CamerasChild.cpp", "dom/media/systemservices/CamerasChild.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e633045eb64aa3935340eda5cacfbedcd5d72110", "parents": ["52bcd064838a6976f80173ce3bcd924c8fb0e6ad"], "tags": []}], "date": 1520278396, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "archaeopteryx@coole-files.de"}, "8816": {"changesets": [{"author": "ffxbld \u003crelease@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "FIREFOX_59b_RELBRANCH", "desc": "Automatic version bump. CLOSED TREE NO BUG a=release", "files": ["browser/config/version_display.txt"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2d10a10c32dc26b6dc0b13ee7805ad6241f82081", "parents": [