\nBackout most of changeset 318f1bcd336e from bug 1329355 to support building releases on buildbot.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: K4QAA8IIpVX", "files": ["toolkit/locales/l10n.mk", "toolkit/mozapps/installer/package-name.mk"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e8bbfbab93d7803a159e0152cb25cf3fffe93171", "parents": ["f0dce5503edddb4451a80dbfe23a999ba496df1e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jeff Walden \u003cjwalden@mit.edu\u003e", "branch": "THUNDERBIRD600b1_2018031401_RELBRANCH", "desc": "Bug 1442967 - Futz with a uintptr_t (as uint32_t) == uint64_t comparison to evade constantly-false compiler warnings in 32-bit builds.  r=jorendorff a=jorgk", "files": ["mfbt/tests/TestEndian.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8852d5a19a3ba028a38dede5db8fa7a7996494c2", "parents": ["e8bbfbab93d7803a159e0152cb25cf3fffe93171"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jeff Walden \u003cjwalden@mit.edu\u003e", "branch": "THUNDERBIRD600b1_2018031401_RELBRANCH", "desc": "Bug 1442967 - When doing a comparison against a 64-bit constant in code run only in 64-bit builds, but compiled in 32-bit builds, cast it to uintptr_t so that the comparison isn't clearly false in 32-bit builds.  rs=froydnj by suggestion on IRC a=jorgk", "files": ["mfbt/tests/TestEndian.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d40ecb1aab22d0a3982155522e7e1a323447f8f8", "parents": ["8852d5a19a3ba028a38dede5db8fa7a7996494c2"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jeff Walden \u003cjwalden@mit.edu\u003e", "branch": "THUNDERBIRD600b1_2018031401_RELBRANCH", "desc": "Bug 1442967 - Boo, MSVC warns when a cast will truncate a numeric constant.  Arguably a desirable warning generally, but here we specifically intend the cast to narrow, so disable the warning.  r=me a=jorgk DONTBUILD", "files": ["mfbt/tests/TestEndian.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "efd290b55a35f8a4ae2958b4300defc1d750ee9e", "parents": ["d40ecb1aab22d0a3982155522e7e1a323447f8f8"], "tags": []}], "date": 1521058812, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null], "user": "mozilla@jorgk.com"}, "8840": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump\n\ngu-IN -\u003e 6211b4a072a5\nhe -\u003e 81a069da9360\nsl -\u003e 5ba9813735ca", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f4a924c0400587066888fc2d8c3cc7b3152ddd4b", "parents": ["f0dce5503edddb4451a80dbfe23a999ba496df1e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Firefox l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump\n\ngu-IN -\u003e 6211b4a072a5\nhe -\u003e 81a069da9360", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5733f4d3acbfd0a62c7643809fed71e7b598de2f", "parents": ["f4a924c0400587066888fc2d8c3cc7b3152ddd4b"], "tags": []}], "date": 1521058826, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "8841": {"changesets": [{"author": "Boris Zbarsky \u003cbzbarsky@mit.edu\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1444231 - Fix QI implementation for FragmentOrElement. r=mccr8 a=jcristau\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 9mPO2ezk2Y7", "files": ["dom/base/Element.cpp", "dom/base/FragmentOrElement.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "925d5693c5a1a73806062947b18c98ed13efc6c3", "parents": ["5733f4d3acbfd0a62c7643809fed71e7b598de2f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jeff Walden \u003cjwalden@mit.edu\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1442967 - Futz with a uintptr_t (as uint32_t) == uint64_t comparison to evade constantly-false compiler warnings in 32-bit builds. r=jorendorff a=test-only", "files": ["mfbt/tests/TestEndian.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5b5c5f82c6d8e49d310687de369649aac6b67c69", "parents": ["925d5693c5a1a73806062947b18c98ed13efc6c3"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jeff Walden \u003cjwalden@mit.edu\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1442967 - When doing a comparison against a 64-bit constant in code run only in 64-bit builds, but compiled in 32-bit builds, cast it to uintptr_t so that the comparison isn't clearly false in 32-bit builds. rs=froydnj by suggestion on IRC a=test-only", "files": ["mfbt/tests/TestEndian.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "960411415e42b8cadfeb60a49e58af3b0dd260d8", "parents": ["5b5c5f82c6d8e49d310687de369649aac6b67c69"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jeff Walden \u003cjwalden@mit.edu\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1442967 - Boo, MSVC warns when a cast will truncate a numeric constant.  Arguably a desirable warning generally, but here we specifically intend the cast to narrow, so disable the warning. r=me in a CLOSED TREE a=test-only", "files": ["mfbt/tests/TestEndian.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e485f830866050893a002e7dcfd5e2ff202b10cc", "parents": ["960411415e42b8cadfeb60a49e58af3b0dd260d8"], "tags": []}], "date": 1521059637, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null], "user": "archaeopteryx@coole-files.de"}, "8842": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump\n\ngu-IN -\u003e e4695687f6bf", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9778baa298b05f5a2292ba3c83f5310ea8936119", "parents": ["e485f830866050893a002e7dcfd5e2ff202b10cc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Firefox l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump\n\nar -\u003e f29cdbff274d\nca -\u003e d3b69d194e1a\net -\u003e 2b88040d0f3c\ngu-IN -\u003e e4695687f6bf\nhu -\u003e 6f48cf9fc7ed\nta -\u003e 405909ac7277", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "gi