003cstandard8@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1446672 - Correctly handle insertion of L10n strings into Places' built-in virtual queries for all bookmarks/left-pane. r=mak a=jcristau", "files": ["toolkit/components/places/nsNavHistory.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "655123cb7bf3f717b01cec5d2774914a15ef433f", "parents": ["e8887d50d037e3fc4c74142e95ef529b1e6025e2"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Justin Wood \u003cCallek@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1446479 - Windows tasks shouldn't try to use the relengapi-proxy. r=tomprince a=RyanVM\nSo, it seems we've (since I landed windows l10n in taskcluster) been using http://relengapi/tooltool/ as the tooltool url, this has only been working because if we have the relevent file in local cache we don't query against tooltool.\n\nWith TC's windows spinup process it fetches a set of tooltool files to cache locally, and this has been saving us, meaning we're very lucky.\n\nHowever maple (beta-based) and central have just diverged in manifests, because central now uses a newer VS version than what we have on maple.\n\nThis patch will fix that to use the new tooltool location that we currently use for Windows builds, and aligns the repackage jobs to use the newer url too.", "files": ["testing/mozharness/configs/repackage/win32_signed.py", "testing/mozharness/configs/repackage/win64_signed.py", "testing/mozharness/configs/single_locale/tc_win32.py", "testing/mozharness/configs/single_locale/tc_win64.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "bd83fe399e698357e5759b799d28c628ad7a1f27", "parents": ["655123cb7bf3f717b01cec5d2774914a15ef433f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mark Striemer \u003cmstriemer@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1444149 - Include addon name and icon in New Tab doorhanger r=aswan a=jcristau l10n=flod\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 2Mpn1iKVPbF", "files": ["browser/components/customizableui/content/panelUI.inc.xul", "browser/components/extensions/ext-url-overrides.js", "browser/locales/en-US/chrome/browser/browser.dtd", "browser/themes/shared/customizableui/panelUI.inc.css", "toolkit/locales/en-US/chrome/global/extensions.properties"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0c9152376d523fa8a03bc8653f5a039b71746be0", "parents": ["bd83fe399e698357e5759b799d28c628ad7a1f27"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mark Striemer \u003cmstriemer@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1444149 - Revert string name change r=flod a=jcristau l10n=flod", "files": ["browser/components/customizableui/content/panelUI.inc.xul", "browser/locales/en-US/chrome/browser/browser.dtd"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "903344884b5546cd939260fcc625051e8f546a86", "parents": ["0c9152376d523fa8a03bc8653f5a039b71746be0"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Shane Caraveo \u003cscaraveo@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1445080 - fix handling of remote web progress for non-tab browsers, r=Gijs,mconley a=jcristau\n\nEnsure remoteWebProgress is initialized for remote browsers.  Includes devtools fix from jryans.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: Ce3TzwkNnyi", "files": ["browser/components/extensions/test/browser/browser_ext_sidebarAction_runtime.js", "devtools/client/responsive.html/browser/swap.js", "toolkit/content/widgets/remote-browser.xml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d95900c76f20660c03d69d7a617e35447a571a40", "parents": ["903344884b5546cd939260fcc625051e8f546a86"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Pehrson \u003cpehrsons@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1443157 - Disregard aData for event recording-device-events. r=johannh a=jcristau\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 8Lo8PWmOAPQ", "files": ["mobile/android/modules/WebrtcUI.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ae0358583eccd3019d6748f43c49df777ad545e6", "parents": ["d95900c76f20660c03d69d7a617e35447a571a40"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Pehrson \u003cpehrsons@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1443803 - Protect against destroyed MediaStream in MediaEngineWebRTCMicrophoneSource. r=padenot a=jcristau\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 3vyzS0DceKI", "files": ["dom/media/webrtc/MediaEngineWebRTCAudio.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "4626b30f8c29a106c1a7876c1a1809107b8b626e", "parents": ["ae0358583eccd3019d6748f43c49df777ad545e6"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Kit Cambridge \u003ckit@yakshaving.ninja\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1441156 - Ensure FxA storage tests don't initialize Sync. r=markh a=jcristau l10n=flod\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: IOtWAkxmbGD", "files": ["services/fxaccounts/FxAccounts.jsm", "services/fxaccounts/tests/xpcshell/test_loginmgr_storage.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7cece7e44b9bc669425349b609e29d71412ce51c", "parents": ["4626b30f8c29a106c1a7876c1a1809107b8b626e"], "tags": []}], "date": 1521477165, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "aiakab@mozilla.com"}, "8873": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jan Beich \u003cjbeich@FreeBSD.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1437670 - Add basic BSD support to GN build. r=dminor f=gaston a=jcristau\n\n- If cross-toolchain is N/A use system one instead of error\n- BSDs often use Linux interfaces, so don't exclude the files\n- Define is_bsd as changes specific to a particular BSD are rare\n- Adjust is_clang in case Gecko would use it in future\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 5LlCbEKbAPO", "files": ["media/webrtc/trunk/build/config/BUILDCONFIG.gn", "media/webrtc/trunk/build/config/ui.gni", "media/webrtc/trunk/build/toolchain/fallback/BUILD.gn"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5d519dfb2238c907f02eefb529e3e7b95c24a254", "parents": ["7cece7e44b9bc669425349b609e29d71412ce51c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Landry Breuil \u003clandry@openbsd.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1437670 - Restore BSD support in WebRTC. r=dminor f=jbeich a=jcristau\n\nOriginal porting was done in bug 807492, so this is mostly gyp-\u003egn translation.\ncflags/libs are left unchanged as those aren't used by Gecko.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: Bhw6KduoiVm", "files": ["media/webrtc/trunk/webrtc/BUILD.gn", "media/webrtc/trunk/webrtc/modules/BUILD.gn", "media/webrtc/trunk/webrtc/modules/video_capture/BUILD.gn", "media/webrtc/trunk/webrtc/system_wrappers/BUILD.gn"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8a093b3af5b598a5490c75f76bc311d4cede968e", "parents": ["5d519dfb2238c907f02eefb529e3e7b95c24a254"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Beich \u003cjbeich@FreeBSD.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1437670 - Add WebRTC's gn-configs for BSDs. r=dminor f=gaston a=jcristau\n\nBased on output from FreeBSD i386/amd64/aarch64 and OpenBSD amd64.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 8D1u28AJTME", "files": ["media/webrtc/gn-configs/arm64_False_arm64_freebsd.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/arm64_True_arm64_freebsd.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/x64_False_x64_dragonfly.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/x64_False_x64_freebsd.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/x64_False_x64_netbsd.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/x64_False_x64_openbsd.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/x64_True_x64_dragonfly.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/x64_True_x64_freebsd.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/x64_True_x64_netbsd.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/x64_True_x64_openbsd.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/x86_False_x86_freebsd.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/x86_False_x86_netbsd.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/x86_False_x86_openbsd.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/x86_True_x86_freebsd.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/x86_True_x86_netbsd.json", "media/webrtc/gn-configs/x86_True_x86_openbsd.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "61411e330c4f61ca1190ed5a5c5126ae5a56281e", "parents": ["8a093b3af5b598a5490c75f76bc311d4cede968e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Beich \u003cjbeich@FreeBSD.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1437670 - Regenerate mozbuild for WebRTC. r=dminor f=gaston a=jcristau\n\nMo