mping Firefox l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump\n\nach -\u003e 45e83d8f0646\nbg -\u003e bde9597fd3ac\nbn-BD -\u003e 93bf8da36d60\nes-CL -\u003e 7f2f9c7f28ab\neu -\u003e 24d0611b96de\nfi -\u003e 4f1fc08e41bb\nfy-NL -\u003e 1422d3664e6f\nka -\u003e a51101627cf7\nlij -\u003e 8197d0a8156b\nnl -\u003e 5d33bcb7f8f4\nnn-NO -\u003e 9c167ab678fa\npl -\u003e 165d482a48be\npt-BR -\u003e 3eed8524fc0a\npt-PT -\u003e 59f722192c48\ntr -\u003e 1196fc548b32", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3ab7468206a10189ae1b4028ef897ab45c8aebe0", "parents": ["9ac03853cc4499a82808d0545017cffe9bbf89b4"], "tags": []}], "date": 1522596079, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "8953": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump\n\ngl -\u003e 53960d5907bf\nhe -\u003e 6deedea70bfc\nth -\u003e f6e4846e9eda", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d07eb2836ce4756ea6410607b2b1572ed2f06dae", "parents": ["3ab7468206a10189ae1b4028ef897ab45c8aebe0"], "tags": []}, {"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Firefox l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump\n\ngl -\u003e 53960d5907bf\nhe -\u003e 6deedea70bfc\nmy -\u003e 08413eeacea5\nth -\u003e d7f21a59a11e", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9cb2fb2d7629c390fd57d6144b432d07e0a541b8", "parents": ["d07eb2836ce4756ea6410607b2b1572ed2f06dae"], "tags": []}], "date": 1522678938, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "8954": {"changesets": [{"author": "Masayuki Nakano \u003cmasayuki@d-toybox.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1435123 - HTMLEditor::GetBlock() has to specify given ancestor limit node to HTMLEditor::GetBlockNodeParent() r=m_kato a=RyanVM\n\nThis is a simple bug of internal API of HTMLEditor.  HTMLEditor::GetBlock()\ntries to retrieve nearest ancestor block node (including itself) of a node.\nHTMLEditor::GetBlock() may have ancestor limiter typically it's active\nediting host to prevent to modify editing host or its ancestor accidentally.\n\nHowever, it forgets to call HTMLEditor::GetBlockNodeParent() with the given\nancestor limit node.  Therefore, if editing host is an inline element and\nits parent is a block element, the editing host is split accidentally.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: Ermmxdnk4KB", "files": ["editor/libeditor/HTMLEditor.cpp", "editor/libeditor/tests/mochitest.ini", "editor/libeditor/tests/test_insertParagraph_in_inline_editing_host.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d0a166d249fbcd024fba7e0b2b3a8bbea35709f3", "parents": ["9cb2fb2d7629c390fd57d6144b432d07e0a541b8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Shane Caraveo \u003cscaraveo@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1446913 - test TabOpen/TabMove event sequence during content click, r=kmag a=RyanVM", "files": ["browser/components/extensions/test/browser/browser_ext_tabs_events.js", "browser/components/extensions/test/browser/file_dummy.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "067a4f15341f5e92a373051e0502851e41ffc83d", "parents": ["d0a166d249fbcd024fba7e0b2b3a8bbea35709f3"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Shane Caraveo \u003cscaraveo@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1446913 - Document and fix event object usage. r=felipe a=RyanVM", "files": ["browser/base/content/browser.js", "browser/base/content/utilityOverlay.js", "browser/modules/ContentClick.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2a46fc9aa444c236b05dd3f6113293e9ad16ca0b", "parents": ["067a4f15341f5e92a373051e0502851e41ffc83d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Botond Ballo \u003cbotond@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1447131 - Handle back