cpearce a=jcristau\n\nAlso ensure that the MP4 demuxer can't create such sample.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: JANgHNiiz2H", "files": ["dom/media/mp4/Index.cpp", "dom/media/platforms/agnostic/bytestreams/AnnexB.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "532e1f4200f9c9dd7f02af68e0e385e5868906d7", "parents": ["b70d5eaa79214e698a7b064b86729701d86b0740"], "tags": []}], "date": 1524154732, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null], "user": "archaeopteryx@coole-files.de"}, "9095": {"changesets": [{"author": "Sebastian Hengst \u003carchaeopteryx@coole-files.de\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1450538 - Add more statuspanel meta data. r=eslint a=eslint-fix", "files": ["browser/base/content/.eslintrc.js", "browser/base/content/moz.build", "browser/base/moz.build"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e6cdf63c59a494a79197fcefca78a83399244a8e", "parents": ["532e1f4200f9c9dd7f02af68e0e385e5868906d7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Dan Minor \u003cdminor@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1437345 - Set defaults for gn visual studio build; r=jesup a=NPOTB\n\nThis hard codes the visual studio version to 2015. We did the same thing for the\ngyp build. It also sets default paths for visual studio, which are ignored by the\nremainder of the build system.\n\nThis was required to get gn code generation working on a fresh install of\nWindows. I must have had similar changes on my old Windows VM but missed\ncommiting them as part of the gyp to gn build switch.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 7fYngpdIwxh", "files": ["media/webrtc/trunk/build/config/win/visual_studio_version.gni"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5988e21167c2913edadb20fa73d7ade380a602f7", "parents": ["e6cdf63c59a494a79197fcefca78a83399244a8e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Beich \u003cjbeich@FreeBSD.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1437345 - Don't try to build audio_device backends. r=dminor a=NPOTB\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: JjLucnqna0A", "files": ["media/w