 Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump\n\nja -\u003e 10449937c3e4\nte -\u003e 97d2c98858b6", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "89247a5ef9ad86a2c263804de191e7c3c305ce24", "parents": ["8fd6beb33a7186a2e5fa06f4ef361c72e0277f09"], "tags": []}, {"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Firefox l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump\n\nja -\u003e 5ba864c5339f\nja-JP-mac -\u003e ab2ad877aa3a\nnl -\u003e c5e98f41ca81\nsl -\u003e 814dac084701", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2b7267563fdbd00009105b17f1bead27ce1dc506", "parents": ["89247a5ef9ad86a2c263804de191e7c3c305ce24"], "tags": []}], "date": 1524482561, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "9120": {"changesets": [{"author": "Brad Werth \u003cbwerth@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1450208: Change nsRange::ExtractRectFromOffset to use simpler, hopefully safer logic to determine whether text is vertical. r=bz a=lizzard\n\nInstead of checking nsIFrame::IsTextFrame() and then casting to nsTextFrame,\nthe new code just checks the writing mode of the frame. Less casts; less\nchance of pointer errors.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: LrtthZjwYq6", "files": ["dom/base/nsRange.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "58ed51bb1575d131be0744e091b3e2c9b8482f6e", "parents": ["2b7267563fdbd00009105b17f1bead27ce1dc506"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Blake Kaplan \u003cmrbkap@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1448200 - Handle the creation of the spellchecker more gracefully. r=Felipe a=lizzard\n\nIf the user right-clicks on an input field and that click causes us to create\na spellchecker, then it won't be initialized in time to show the context menu.\nHandle that case more gracefully by passing that state up to the parent.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 1hjxloq2OLp", "files": ["toolkit/modules/InlineSpellCheckerContent.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c12a2478a5c0db017085474168a74edab2c07f44", "parents": ["58ed51bb1575d131be0744e091b3e2c9b8482f6e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andrew Osmond \u003caosmond@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1452467 - Make native font resource memory allocations fallible. r=lsalzman a=lizzard", "files": ["gfx/2d/NativeFontResourceDWrite.cpp", "gfx/2d/NativeFontResourceFontconfig.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c408410b77e1ffed613d91f6c56540eb24823182", "parents": ["c12a2478a5c0db017085474168a74edab2c07f44"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Masatoshi Kimura \u003cVYV03354@nifty.ne.jp\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1450538 - Use nsIURI::GetDisplaySpec to compensate a change to nsIURI::GetSpec. r=valentin a=jcristau\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 5xYAbx78K3q", "files": ["docshell/base/nsDocShell.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "455ece02d8d2b05d144f1b56308376854a313708", "parents": ["c408410b77e1ffed613d91f6c56540eb24823182"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Valentin Gosu \u003cvalentin.gosu@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1450199 - Cookie is not synced across tabs r=Ehsan a=lizzard\n\nThis patch reverts parts of changeset e87e706def11 (bug 1425031).\nThe problem in bug 1425031 was that when the content process set a cookie\na notification was sent to the parent process. This notification was then\nforwarded to all the content processes, including the one it originated from.\nThe solution was to not forward cookies that originated from a content\nprocess, but this causes the current bug.\nThe correct fix is to forward the cookie changes to all content processes\nexcept the one they originated from.\nThe test for bug 1425031 remains, and should keep passing.\n\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 1P6JwHQDy93", "files": ["dom/ipc/ContentParent.cpp", "netwerk/cookie/CookieServiceParent.cpp", "netwerk/cookie/CookieServiceParent.h", "netwerk/cookie/nsCookieService.cpp", "netwerk/cookie/nsCookieService.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6bda4eb052298c6abc57ef9da82ef59c97d5591f", "parents": ["455ece02d8d2b05d144f1b56308376854a313708"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Zibi Braniecki \u003czbraniecki@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1454323 - Set the default key in \u003ckey\u003e to avoid it capturing all command keys. r=jaws a=jcristau\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 3oD7iaTEbZg", "files": ["browser/components/preferences/in-content/preferences.xul"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "49d46c15ca0b43bd6b8e44a1667e5edfcd40cd0d", "parents": ["6bda4eb052298c6abc57ef9da82ef59c97d5591f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Christoph Kerschbaumer \u003cckerschb@christophkerschbaumer.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1454914: Exempt web-extensions from same-site cookie policy. r=valentin,kmag a=jcristau", "files": ["netwerk/base/nsNetUtil.cpp", "netwerk/cookie/nsCookieService.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e4f5887e03314fd90d9466b280344d2baf0ff2bb", "parents": ["49d46c15ca0b43bd6b8e44a1667e5edfcd40cd0d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Christoph Kerschbaumer \u003cckerschb@christophkerschbaumer.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1454914: Test web extensions are exempt from samesite cookie policy.r=jkt a=jcristau", "files": ["toolkit/components/extensions/test/mochitest/file_same_site_cookies_webextension.sjs", "toolkit/components/extensions/test/mochitest/mochitest-common.ini", "toolkit/components/extensions/test/mochitest/test_same_site_cookies_webextension.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "efbf62fe77578780db3cadfac8c13e9c4e8a5fef", "parents": ["e4f5887e03314fd90d9466b280344d2baf0ff2bb"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Michael Kaply \u003cmozilla@kaply.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "