\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1406727 - more checks. r=mstange a=lizzard", "files": ["layout/generic/nsGfxScrollFrame.cpp", "layout/painting/nsDisplayList.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "bda9a66dc3583e484c42c77089160a2af9441a0b", "parents": ["e21076f36898f0677d2e9026dd1df5115d0b46ba"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan de Mooij \u003cjdemooij@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1447989 - Sweep script types in TypeMonitorResult. r=tcampbell a=lizzard", "files": ["js/src/vm/TypeInference.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "faa0174ca76eefb9fe36c9bd0150e4c91f825170", "parents": ["bda9a66dc3583e484c42c77089160a2af9441a0b"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Martin Stransky \u003cstransky@redhat.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1355143 - Implement CreateStyleContextWithStates to style with fully stated css path, r=jhorak a=lizzard\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: ENWBekzq4Oq", "files": ["widget/gtk/WidgetStyleCache.cpp", "widget/gtk/WidgetStyleCache.h", "widget/gtk/mozgtk/mozgtk.c"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "eede6015f82c49b9cd9f4f1e889fc92a40fdd82d", "parents": ["faa0174ca76eefb9fe36c9bd0150e4c91f825170"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Martin Stransky \u003cstransky@redhat.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1355143 - Provide ScrollbarGTKMetrics for active (mouse over) scrollbars, r=jhorak a=lizzard\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 95d1jeQ8mXd", "files": ["widget/gtk/gtk3drawing.cpp", "widget/gtk/gtkdrawing.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "48abba26dc258cafb197abe6d8a59303b41bc5f7", "parents": ["eede6015f82c49b9cd9f4f1e889fc92a40fdd82d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Martin Stransky \u003cstransky@redhat.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1355143 - Size scrollbars with 'hover' Gtk+ state, r=jhorak a=lizzard\n\nUbuntu/Ambiance has tiny scrollbars when it's not hovered by mouse and large\nones when it's hovered/active. Our current Gtk+ toolkit code does not support such scrollbar\nresize on the fly.\n\nWe use a workaround as we get size of active (hovered) scrollbar only and that\nwe pass to gecko. Then we draw scrolbar smaller when it's not hovered and full sized\nwhen it's hovered.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: mxt9q5Bcg9", "files": ["widget/gtk/nsNativeThemeGTK.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8aabde7e8df2c0588a67da9b28383eed18e03ac7", "parents": ["48abba26dc258cafb197abe6d8a59303b41bc5f7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Kartikaya Gupta \u003ckgupta@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1430813 - Prevent scenario where we keep a dead frame pointer on the EventStateManager. r=smaug a=lizzard\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: HN8XgsMGisy", "files": ["layout/base/PresShell.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a11d711ad7d1ee0d6b2c0b603f03229d8fe2b90e", "parents": ["8aabde7e8df2c0588a67da9b28383eed18e03ac7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Aaron Klotz \u003caklotz@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1455110: Replace RegOpenKeyEx/RegQueryValueEx with RegGetValue; r=jimm a=lizzard", "files": ["toolkit/xre/nsAppRunner.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f2d63307f232559c9e3c92ce13edeaac27460c48", "parents": ["a11d711ad7d1ee0d6b2c0b603f03229d8fe2b90e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "David Parks \u003cdparks@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1451452 - Properly display plugin settings checkboxes. r=Mossop a=lizzard\n\nSome settings should show the box as checked when set and some should show it as not checked.  This patch handles the inversion.", "files": ["toolkit/mozapps/extensions/content/pluginPrefs.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "dd61ef4a8a42b600b02eace99baa04ad2a56cc55", "parents": ["f2d63307f232559c9e3c92ce13edeaac27460c48"], "tags": []}], "date": 1524636882, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "archaeopteryx@coole-files.de"}, "9145": {"changesets": [{"author": "Eric Rah